snippet.title: Flamberge - January 2017 Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Hi everyone! Ben and I put out a new build yesterday (1/9/2017) and we're really proud of it. Special thanks to the folks who came by our booth at MAGFest and helped test the game.

Kickstarter Update - https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hydezeke/flamberge/posts/1780821?ref=email

Steam page -
http://store.steampowered.com/app/355420
